name: Tenki Hybrid
description:
This model functions as a bit of a hybrid compared to my others. Based on loras and prompting, it can handle 2D, near-2.5D, and everything in-between!

My usual settings:

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras
Sample Steps: 20-35
Upscaler: ESRGAN_4x
Deniose: 0.5
CFG: 5-9
Vae: Grapefruit vae

By no means is this law, feel free to experiment and I'd love to see your results!!

For inpainting, I generally limit to Only Masked to 800 x 800 or lower and 0.5 denoise (or lower if you want to maintain the initial face look more). It will start to get a little too detailed at higher res'. You shouldn't need to change your prompt at all when inpainting faces to get a good result.

Same as my other models, it plays very well with artist style loras!
